            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> Aelia Mo<lb break="no" n="2"/><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>etiana</ex></expan> Nerat<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>o b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciario</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>uni</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXVII <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Surus b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>pr<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>ef</abbr><ex>ecti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>le</abbr><ex>gionis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eiusd</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Oneratus <lb n="8"/>bene mere<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>ti</abbr></expan> <lb n="9"/>posuerunt
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Erhaltene ist in zwei Teile gebrochen. Auf der linken Nebenseite Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes die Büsten einer Frau und eines Mannes sowie eines Knaben dazwischen; in den oberen Ecken je ein Delphin. Z. 1 befindet sich auf dem Rahmen zwischen Inschrift- und Bildfeld. Z. 3: Buchstabe N spiegelverkehrt. (B): Schallmayer - Eibl - Ott - Preuss - Wittkopf: Z. 3: Neratio; CIL III: Z. 6: Iu(lius).</p>
            </div>
